{"tid":1556011,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【必睇！●和班非勇武對談Q&A】合作有爭拗 默契靠摸索","createTime":"2019-09-09T14:35:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-09T14:43:30.000Z","uid":68738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9489cd49365dd4ee1465704bb1570c552c2b155d","tid":1556011,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190908/large/1567938544_b0a2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190908%2Flarge%2F1567938544_b0a2.png&h=ec4e1461&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n彭志行攝(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n記：記者　N：N（勇武）　R：Ronald（和理非）<br />\n<br />\n記：點睇和理非或冷氣軍師叫「散水」？<br />\n<br />\nN：周不時有人叫散水，我哋都明嘅，佢哋怕我哋受傷，但係前線其實會自己衡量係咪要走，真係被人拉嗰個係我哋，咁大個人有判斷能力，總之各自努力。一切後果我哋會自己承擔，在場爭拗都無謂。要互相尊重，畀意見係OK，但係唔好帶隊走。<br />\n<br />\nR：試過有次和理非同勇武都在場，和理非呢邊覺得當日目的已達成，留低無意義，點解唔退場？我哋想說服佢哋，大家圍圈傾。後來得出共識，勇武唔會主動衝擊，但佢哋同我哋講，話因為情況隨時有變，所以佢哋會守到最後一刻。其實我之前真係冇諗過原來佢哋咁諗，實際討論後，知道佢哋每人都有好清楚嘅諗法，有啲本來只係想勸人走嘅反而留低咗。勇武唔只得個勇字，佢哋有思考，反而和理非都未必一定好理性。<br />\n<br />\nN：冷氣軍師同和理非都係出於善意，但唔好幫前線決定去留。<br />\n<br />\n提供即時資訊 前線自決<br />\n<br />\n記：咁作為前線你覺得可以點同和理非協調？<br />\n<br />\nN：第一，佢哋可以幫手提供即時資訊，好重要㗎！例如幾個街口後有咩發生，有冇水炮車、係咪已被警方包抄，前線一般好忙，未必顧到其他嘢，畀多啲現場資訊前線，等佢哋自己決定點做。<br />\n<br />\n另外就係如果冇gear、心理未準備好，就唔好因為八卦而走上前線，咁樣對前線手足嚟講好危險。防暴衝上嚟，如果你panic到企喺度唔識郁，要人救你就唔係太好。而家警方策略係一放彈就衝過嚟拉人，滅煙同前線需要好多空間，後排支持我哋嘅和理非朋友可以企鬆少少，畀多啲空間我哋，亦唔好上前打卡湊熱鬧。<br />\n<br />\n第三，企後排嘅其實唔使咁驚，若防暴有少少舉動你哋就尖叫，會帶動其他人情緒，令其他人更驚，咁樣反而令大家唔安全。<br />\n<br />\nR：到底雙方點樣合作，我都成日諗呢個問題，初時和理非唔理解，但合作係靠摸索出嚟嘅，心態好重要。<br />\n<br />\n記：相反，前線可以點幫和理非？<br />\n<br />\nN：2014年已做緊，一方面拖延防暴推進，畀多啲時間和平示威人士撤離，另一方面係將我哋同警方嘅武力不對等差距縮窄，警方無論喺武器、技巧、裝備上一定贏。我哋無大台、無一個靈魂人物，所有人都一定要不停思考！每一刻都要冷靜分析，唔可以懶！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190909/60023643?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190909%2F60023643%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=3833d9b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190909%2F60023643%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_2&h=f709da7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190909/60023643?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_2</a>"},{"pid":"bd8f7592e6ce8862b9a61eee38bd3021c1b52c42","tid":1556011,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:37:24.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣【牆紙！】<br />\n<br />\n第四期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1547783/page/1</a><br />\n第三期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1519434/page/1</a><br />\n第二期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1498347/page/1</a><br />\n第一期Link : <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1479130/page/1</a><br />\nTG CHANNEL :<a href=\"https://t.me/WallPaperENews\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FWallPaperENews&d=e21%2BqJk643s04YHbVA6HNkBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=724e471c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/WallPaperENews</a>"},{"pid":"1c49b46ed26d8afcdc8c2c70a3338c1baf3c317c","tid":1556011,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cb296ddee96d50b0c9bb5152ccb70e495ec3011","tid":1556011,"uid":68738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:38:12.000Z","msg":"佢哋可以幫手提供即時資訊，好重要㗎！例如幾個街口後有咩發生，有冇水炮車、係咪已被警方包抄，前線一般好忙，未必顧到其他嘢，畀多啲現場資訊前線，等佢哋自己決定點做。<br />\n<br />\n好重要 特別係冷氣軍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2e82b585c932f62c66f467776b307cd61b4e242","tid":1556011,"uid":5523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:40:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7155c3c30302d6bc5158c8cfd2f69a5a3780bbd4","tid":1556011,"uid":68738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-09T14:43:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}